{
  "3328480": {
    "name": "TETRIS® THE GRAND MASTER 4 -ABSOLUTE EYE-",
    "steam_appid": 3328480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/07ddd7cdd40eba432518bc84deec3692.avif?t=1770178936\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras_big/07ddd7cdd40eba432518bc84deec3692.avif?t=1770178936 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1998年8月，在游戏中心登场的动作益智游戏『TETRIS® THE GRAND MASTER』，作为专为核心玩家打造、充满深度可挖掘要素的『Tetris』，赢得了众多粉丝的喜爱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >之后，2000年推出了『TETRIS THE ABSOLUTE THE GRAND MASTER 2』，2005年发行了『TETRIS THE GRAND MASTER 3 -Terror Instinct-』，时隔20年，系列最新作『TETRIS THE GRAND MASTER 4 -ABSOLUTE EYE-』将登陆Steam。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/94312c5d536bd9ccf12119b133b7000d.avif?t=1770178936\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras_big/94312c5d536bd9ccf12119b133b7000d.avif?t=1770178936 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这次的『TGM4』提供了更加深入、更具战略性的『Tetris』体验，丰富的深度足以满足广大玩家。在新增的模式中，需要缜密的策略与高速操作，你的技巧将被推向极限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，也搭载了让Tetris新手也能轻松享受的模式，往往会让人不知不觉地一次次重试，充满令人着迷的魅力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的音乐由『TGM』系列的老面孔细江慎治先生负责。他所谱写的紧张而又激昂的音乐将提升玩家的专注力，让游戏氛围更加热血澎湃。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※玩家之间可以通过本地游玩进行对战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/fce53942e7f649f33ce2e8bffbf9d8b1.avif?t=1770178936\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏模式介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在『TETRIS THE GRAND MASTER 4 -ABSOLUTE EYE-』中收录了以下游戏模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/566c86d3bd432327d045631927613d73.webp?t=1770178936\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MARATHON</strong>: 这是一般的『Tetris』模式，以挑战最高分为目标（可使用“STANDARD”操作方式游玩）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/231753fe51e93edbcfe23acd54545bab.avif?t=1770178936\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras_big/231753fe51e93edbcfe23acd54545bab.avif?t=1770178936 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/0de1c43ad01bb7d453a7a6da5dfe7271.webp?t=1770178936\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NORMAL</strong>: 同样是一般的『Tetris』模式，但比拼谁能用最短时间消除行（可使用“TGM”操作方式游玩）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/d1acf0764838c7e3c62da570b0ceb6bd.avif?t=1770178936\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras_big/d1acf0764838c7e3c62da570b0ceb6bd.avif?t=1770178936 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/27495be18838bedca224cea899ec5540.webp?t=1770178936\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ASUKA</strong>: 面向中级玩家的模式。方块会以最高速度下落，需要迅速放置并消行，并在限定时间内挑战能够达到多高的等级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/c68842264bcc6b8d52bcdc6454fc9453.avif?t=1770178936\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras_big/c68842264bcc6b8d52bcdc6454fc9453.avif?t=1770178936 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，ASUKA模式还配备了回溯功能。可以利用倒带功能，回到方块刚下落时的状态重新进行操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/5f1ecd1d521c6fa80d43bfa63af3b40d.poster.avif?t=1770178936\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/5f1ecd1d521c6fa80d43bfa63af3b40d.webm?t=1770178936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/5f1ecd1d521c6fa80d43bfa63af3b40d.mp4?t=1770178936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/ffd0a1fae43eae99ceaf870b042ff628.webp?t=1770178936\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MASTER</strong>: 面向高级玩家，考验所有『Tetris』技巧的模式。目标是尽可能提升等级。游戏开始时就会以最高速度下落方块，需要巧妙地堆叠并消行。请充分运用T旋转（T-Spins）和全消等各种技巧来挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/0c2af48b8e9db4e9ee1f342426bc942a.avif?t=1770178936\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras_big/0c2af48b8e9db4e9ee1f342426bc942a.avif?t=1770178936 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/4c822176d5c336cc596b2d0143867c1c.webp?t=1770178936\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KONOHA</strong>: 这是一个使用大型方块进行游戏的模式。每次完成全部消除时，会解锁奖励插图。在游戏初期，会显示帮助完成全部消除的指南。完成全部消除后，奖励插图会逐渐解锁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/93447c27c5b03767b0996584ae06203e.avif?t=1770178936\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras_big/93447c27c5b03767b0996584ae06203e.avif?t=1770178936 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁的插图可以在KONOHA角色图鉴中查看。让我们以解锁全部角色为目标吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/4ac4ca334ed95ad5de52cb61a5028ddd.avif?t=1770178936\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras_big/4ac4ca334ed95ad5de52cb61a5028ddd.avif?t=1770178936 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/ff16bab09db307ad469da7d6f08a9660.webp?t=1770178936\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SHIRANUI</strong>: 可以与CPU对战的模式。请尽力击败具有各种思考方式的CPU，目标是战胜最高难度的CPU。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/7b1f2bbff7a0974aee2972a554964e1c.avif?t=1770178936\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras_big/7b1f2bbff7a0974aee2972a554964e1c.avif?t=1770178936 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若能战胜CPU，即可解锁更多后续等级。通常难度（Tier）越高，CPU就越强。而且，在特定条件下可能还会出现隐藏难度……!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras/a09b658ba78330d6bf5fa21a59393d66.avif?t=1770178936\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328480/extras_big/a09b658ba78330d6bf5fa21a59393d66.avif?t=1770178936 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
